 <span data-ttu-id="39c1f-294">`alternateChoices` viene aggiunto alla fine della sequenza corrente di elementi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="39c1f-294">`alternateChoices` is added to the end of the current sequence of elements.</span></span>  
  
